title: Hour 1 - Monday Night Football
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Monday Night Football
description:
On today's edition of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan and the Danette's talk about their takeaway's from last night's Monday Night Football doubleheader featuring the Titans taking on the Bills and the Vikings visiting the Eagles.
